            <description><![CDATA[【世界防治肥胖日，收好这份减肥人必备攻略】<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23BMI%E6%80%8E%E4%B9%88%E7%AE%97%E6%80%8E%E4%B9%88%E7%9C%8B%23&amp;extparam=%23BMI%E6%80%8E%E4%B9%88%E7%AE%97%E6%80%8E%E4%B9%88%E7%9C%8B%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#BMI怎么算怎么看#</span></a>边运动打卡边熬夜、觉得出汗多就是燃脂、主食一概不吃…你知道吗？这些都是减肥误区。其实，<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E7%9D%A1%E4%B8%8D%E5%A4%9F%E4%BC%9A%E5%AF%BC%E8%87%B4%E8%82%A5%E8%83%96%23&amp;extparam=%23%E7%9D%A1%E4%B8%8D%E5%A4%9F%E4%BC%9A%E5%AF%BC%E8%87%B4%E8%82%A5%E8%83%96%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#睡不够会导致肥胖#</span></a>、碳水摄入不足影响新陈代谢…世界防治肥胖日，掌握管住嘴迈开腿的正确方式👇🏻收好不谢<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[doge]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_doge-be7f768d78.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>（人民日报） <img style="" src="https://wx2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hdu9f0arb8j20rs0u6afh.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hdu9f0s2pbj20rs0u543v.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hdu9f19wpaj20rs10y48w.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hdu9ezyq0ij20rs0ysjzr.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hdu9f1qxeij20rs0yrdnv.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hdu9f22pevj20rr0yrgtn.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hdu9f2hpuzj20rs0yrjyy.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hdu9f2tffij20rs0ytn3w.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hdu9f3d060j20rs0yq7d2.jpg" referrerpolicy="no