            <description><![CDATA[【学起！<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%B8%AD%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B4%E9%A2%88%E6%A4%8E%E5%81%A5%E8%BA%AB%E6%93%8D%23&amp;extparam=%23%E4%B8%AD%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B4%E9%A2%88%E6%A4%8E%E5%81%A5%E8%BA%AB%E6%93%8D%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#中青年颈椎健身操#</span></a><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[赢牛奶]" src="https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/9c/2021_yingniunai_org.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】常常低头刷手机的你，颈椎还好吗？当你出现颈背疼痛、手指发麻、行走困难、头晕、恶心甚至视物模糊等症状时，可能颈椎已经出现问题。长时间<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%88%B7%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%BA%E6%9C%89%E5%AE%8C%E7%BE%8E%E5%A7%BF%E5%8A%BF%E5%90%97%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%88%B7%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%BA%E6%9C%89%E5%AE%8C%E7%BE%8E%E5%A7%BF%E5%8A%BF%E5%90%97%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#刷手机有完美姿势吗#</span></a>？怎样缓解颈椎疼痛？戳👇🏻骨科专家推荐的颈椎健身操<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[加油]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_jiayou-a34ced0409.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a> （人民日报） <img style="" src="https://wx1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hdt0vip0rgj20j60qi771.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hdt0viyyb7j20j60tgadp.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hdt0vjab5uj20j60owwgy.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hdt0vjk0d2j20j60nrgo7.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hdt0vjukygj20j60nrdid.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-re